= The Catholic Commitee

In an effort to act as a counterweight to the growing strength of the Rural People's Movement, the bulk of organised agrculture has formed an umbrella organisation called the <span style="color: #0dba1e;">**Green Front**</span>, affording agricultural interests in the <span style="color: #000000;">**Center Party**</span> and <span style="color: #3E88B3;">**DNVP**</span> more influence in their respective parties.
Built on the negotiations back in March, the <span style="color: #0dba1e;">**Green Front**</span> aims for the economic rehabiltion of the German farmer in the face of growing economic hardship.
With members from the <span style="color: #3E88B3;">**DNVP**</span>, <span style="color: #006400;">**CNBLP**</span> and <span style="color: #909090;">**DBP**</span>, this disparate coalition is testament to the increasingly concering plight of farmers in the countryside.
[? if agriculture_minister_party = 'Z': As we currently hold the Agriculture Ministry, the onus falls on us to implement the <span style="color: #0dba1e;">**Green Front**</span>'s economic program in the coming months. ?] This increased focus on agricultural issues might alienate our substantial worker base while this extensive cooperation with anti-republican parties has led to outcry from the left of the party.
